|3 | SUBPLAN FILTER        |    |4        |115 |
|4 |  TABLE SCAN           |t2  |7        |38  |
|5 |  LIMIT                |    |1        |77  |
|6 |   MERGE UNION DISTINCT|    |1        |77  |
|7 |    SORT               |    |1        |38  |
|8 |     LIMIT             |    |1        |38  |
|9 |      HASH DISTINCT    |    |1        |38  |
|10|       TABLE SCAN      |t1  |2        |36  |
|11|    SORT               |    |1        |38  |
|12|     LIMIT             |    |1        |38  |
|13|      HASH DISTINCT    |    |1        |38  |
|14|       TABLE SCAN      |t1  |2        |36  |
================================================

